&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;idwzal&quot; data-start=&quot;1622&quot; data-end=&quot;1733&quot;&gt;Master’s degree in Supply Chain Management, Logistics, Business Administration, or a related field preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
