&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1fswa1v&quot; data-start=&quot;1983&quot; data-end=&quot;2096&quot;&gt;Strong analytical, problem-solving, and escalation management skills in fast-paced transportation environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;jzmpf4&quot; data-start=&quot;2097&quot; data-end=&quot;2204&quot; data-is-last-node=&quot;&quot;&gt;Ability to work weekends and flexible schedules as required by business demands and operational workload.&lt;/li&gt;
